urls.title: Air Canada to Acquire 15 Additional Canadian-built Airbus A220-300 Aircraft
urls.description: Airline converts options to bring to 60 its total confirmed A220 order Advances Air Canada's modernization program for more fuel-efficient fleet MONTREAL, Oct. 26, 2022 /CNW Telbec/ - Air Canada...

data.text:
We're buying 15 more Canadian-built @Airbus #A220-300 planes, so we'll have 60 in our fleet, further supporting jobs in our country’s vital aerospace sector. All of our A220s are built in Mirabel, Quebec. 
More: https://t.co/lwNPCXAZ0M https://t.co/WiAsMWrIR0
